(7, 1, '2013-01-03 09:09:47', '2013-01-03 09:09:47', '<!--?php while ( have_posts() ) : the_post(); ?-->\n<!-- Header Slide image Starts -->\n<div class="slider-wrap innerheader"><img src="&lt;?php bloginfo(''template_directory''); ?&gt;/images/header_faqs.jpg" alt="" />\n<div class="titleTxt">\n<h4>FAQs</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Header Slide image Ends -->\n\n<!-- Main Content Starts -->\n<div class="content-wrap bg_shadow">\n<div class="container"><!-- Left Content Home Starts -->\n<div class="container_three_forth border_right"><!--First Three Columns Starts--><section class="service-columns clearfix">&lt;h1 &gt;FAQs\n<div class="faqdiv sep_hor">\n<p class="question">What are the actions of Happy Camera Club ?</p>\n\n<div class="answer">\n\nby teaching not so privileged basic aspects of skill like photography which further can be used by them in their day to day life.\n\n\n\n\nPhotography and photo editing (software skills) are practical skills which potentially increase chances of students towards employment. In the same time it gives children chance to explore their creativity and self-expression. Learning how to build portfolio and interaction in the group is surely relevant social experience which can help to build positive self-image and confidence/skills in social interactions.\n\n</div>\n<div class="clearfix sep_hor"></div>\n<p class="question">Why ?</p>\n\n<div class="answer">\n\nWe don''t have an answer to it. It just came from within. It was very passionate.\nRather than hearing all sorts of stories and mulling over it ,we wanted to act.\nIt was a proactive decision. To do something meaningful with whatever resources we had with us instead of waiting for things to happen.\nÂ» To have a passion is good\n\nÂ» To follow what you are passionate about is great\n\nÂ» To make a living out of it is best\n\n</div>\n<div class="clearfix sep_hor"></div>\n<p class="question">How ?</p>\n\n<div class="answer">\n\nWith dignity. ( we believe in the power of each individual to be the change. We look for empowerment of the individual not dependency . Just because of the bad luck of their situation doesn''t mean they should be without options)\n\n\n\nThrough effective management . ( though we have scant resources effectively it works to our advantage. Right from arranging the cameras to collecting the images and then rolling out the prints . we look at technology to solve the challenges)\n\n\n\nUsing Photography as a tool (Taking the alternative choice of medium and go beyond the straight jacketed way of thinking )\n\n</div>\n<div class="clearfix sep_hor"></div>\n<p class="question">What does it aim to achieve ?</p>\n\n<div class="answer">\n\na) To understand oneself and build self expression by learning a skill set that not only is meaningful but also interesting to implement i.e photography\n\n\n\nb) Social inclusion . Photography as a medium has the power to go beyond the usual society norms.\n\n\n\nc) Provide a possible means of livelihoods through individual empowerment\n\n</div>\n<div class="clearfix sep_hor"></div>\n<p class="question">Nature of workshops ?</p>\n\n<div class="answer">\n\nEach workshop usually last for a month culminating in a body of work taken by students. During these workshops the students learn various aspects of photography ,though many of them holding the camera for the first time are quite happy just to press the button !!\n\n\n\nWe teach using point and shoot cameras and are always in need of a fewâ¦\n\n</div>\n<div class="clearfix sep_hor"></div>\n<p class="question">Do we charge the students taking workshops ?</p>\n\n<div class="answer">\n\nNo. The classes are free of cost. Our students are coming from backgrounds that are n''t relatively well off. So we aim to support them through our own means. We expect the organizations, individuals who work alongside us to support financially and operationally in organizing the workshops.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n<!-- Left Content Home Ends -->\n<!--?php get_sidebar-faq(); ?-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Main Content Ends -->\n\n<!--Page wrap Ends-->\n<!--?php endwhile; // end of the loop. ?-->', 'FAQs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '5-autosave', '', '', '2013-01-03 09:09:47', '2013-01-03 09:09:47', '', 5, 'http://localhost/hc/?p=7', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
