(110, 1, '2013-01-10 06:14:56', '2013-01-10 06:14:56', 'We donât have an answer to it. It just came from within. It was very passionate.\r\nRather than hearing all sorts of stories and mulling over it ,we wanted to act.\r\nIt was a proactive decision. To do something meaningful with whatever resources we had with us instead of waiting for things to happen.\r\n			&raquo; To have a passion is good<br>\r\n			&raquo; To follow what you are passionate about is great<br>\r\n			&raquo; To make a living out of it is best', 'Why ?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why', '', '', '2013-01-10 06:14:56', '2013-01-10 06:14:56', '', 0, 'http://web.happycameraclub.com/?post_type=question&#038;p=110', 0, 'question', '', 0),
(111, 1, '2013-01-10 06:15:30', '2013-01-10 06:15:30', 'With dignity.  ( we believe in the power of each individual to be the change. We look for empowerment of the individual not dependency . Just because of the bad luck of their situation doesnât mean they should be without options)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThrough effective management . ( though we have scant resources effectively it works to our advantage. Right from arranging the cameras to collecting the images and then rolling out the prints . we look at technology to solve the challenges)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nUsing Photography as a tool (Taking the alternative choice of medium and go beyond the straight jacketed way of thinking )', 'How ?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how', '', '', '2013-01-10 06:15:30', '2013-01-10 06:15:30', '', 0, 'http://web.happycameraclub.com/?post_type=question&#038;p=111', 0, 'question', '', 0),
(112, 1, '2013-01-10 06:16:17', '2013-01-10 06:16:17', 'a) To understand oneself and build self expression by learning a skill set that not only is meaningful but also interesting to implement i.e photography\r\n\r\nb) Social inclusion . Photography as a medium has the power to go beyond the usual society norms.\r\n\r\nc) Provide a possible means of livelihoods through individual empowerment', 'What does it aim to achieve ?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-does-it-aim-to-achieve', '', '', '2013-01-10 06:16:44', '2013-01-10 06:16:44', '', 0, 'http://web.happycameraclub.com/?post_type=question&#038;p=112', 0, 'question', '', 0),
(113, 1, '2013-01-10 06:17:09', '2013-01-10 06:17:09', 'Each workshop usually last for a month culminating in a body of work taken by students. During these workshops the students learn various aspects of photography ,though many of them holding the camera for the first time are quite happy just to press the button !!&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\nWe teach using point and shoot cameras and are always in need of a fewâ¦', 'Nature of workshops ?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nature-of-workshops', '', '', '2013-01-10 06:17:09', '2013-01-10 06:17:09', '', 0, 'http://web.happycameraclub.com/?post_type=question&#038;p=113', 0, 'question', '', 0),
