(126, 1, '2013-01-11 05:20:47', '2013-01-11 05:20:47', 'We don''t have an answer to it. It just came from within. It was very passionate.\r\nRather than hearing all sorts of stories and mulling over it ,we wanted to act.\r\nIt was a proactive decision. To do something meaningful with whatever resources we had with us instead of waiting for things to happen.\r\n			&raquo; To have a passion is good<br>\r\n			&raquo; To follow what you are passionate about is great<br>\r\n			&raquo; To make a living out of it is best', 'Why ?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why', '', '', '2013-01-11 05:20:47', '2013-01-11 05:20:47', '', 0, 'http://web.happycameraclub.com/?p=126', 0, 'post', '', 0),
